1. Files
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
The following files should be present:

	input.json
	lib/
		json_simple-1.1.jar
	make.bat
	makefile
	README.txt
	report.pdf
	src/
		cs2510/
			Main.java
			Message.java
			Request.java
			Server.java
			stats.java

2. Compiling
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
We provide both a makefile and a windows batch file to make compilation easy.
Simply type "make" to compile the source files.


3. Running
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
We provide both a makefile and a windows batch file to make program execution
easy. Simply type "make run" to run the program. The program searches for a
file named "input.json".

* to run the centralized algorithm, type "make centralized"
* to run the distributed algorithm, type "make distributed"

